# 📝 boAt Lifestyle – Signup Page

This is the **multi-step signup UI** for the boAt Lifestyle project. Built using only HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, it offers an elegant onboarding experience for new users with modern validation, password strength indicator, and user preferences.

---

## 📂 File Included
