│
├── js/
│   ├── main.js           
│   ├── login.js          
│   └── signup.js  
 # Complete Signup Form UI
No external libraries or frameworks are required.

🎯 Features
#MultiStepForm (3 steps)

#ResponsiveDesign

#PasswordStrengthChecker

#CustomValidation

#UserInterestsSelector

#TermsAgreement

#CSSAnimations

#SignupFlowUX

🧩 Step Breakdown
✅ Step 1: Account Details
First & Last Name

Email (with format validation)

Password & Confirm Password

Password visibility toggle

Password strength meter

👤 Step 2: Personal Information
Phone, Date of Birth

Gender (select dropdown)

Address, City, Pincode

🎵 Step 3: Preferences & Agreements
Select music interests (multi-select)

Newsletter & promotional checkbox

Terms & Privacy Policy confirmation

🛠 How to Use
Open signup.html in any modern web browser.

Fill in the fields, navigate between steps using Next / Previous.

Click Create Account on the final step to simulate signup.

⚠️ Note: This is a front-end only demo. No data is stored or submitted to a server.

📸 UI Highlights
Clean and modern UI with brand-aligned gradients

Works on both desktop and mobile (media queries)

Input validation & visual feedback

Smooth transitions and visual step indicators

🚀 Future Enhancements
Connect to backend (e.g., Supabase, Firebase)

Integrate real signup logic and data storage

Add email verification & OTP

Replace alerts with modal dialogs

